    "shortCode": "DV_EUMgjb7R",
    "caption": "@claudeai used to give me ui that technically worked but felt dead. \n\nno motion and no micro interactions. buttons that just appear instead of animate. everything looked flat and lifeless.\n\nI\u2019d look at the output and think yeah it\u2019s fine but it doesn\u2019t feel like anything. no personality and no craft. \n\nnone of the small details that make you go \u201coh that\u2019s nice.\u201d\n\nthen I added 7 things to my setup and everything shifted. shadows feel softer. animations feel smooth. transitions actually have purpose. even the spacing between elements feels more intentional.\n\nit\u2019s the tiny stuff that separates good ui from ui that makes people feel something. swipe to see all 7. \n\nthey\u2019re free and they completely changed my output.\n\nif you care about craft, code, and building interfaces that feel good, follow\u00a0@mirayatech\n\n#claude #ai #design #code #developer",
